desc: A place for unique, upcycled, fun, and funky accessories. Tantalizing tassels, winsome wire jewelry, and masks for everyone! From sweet skulls to precious stones and pearls, we specialize in custom colorways and bridal pieces. Contact us for more info on custom pieces or if you'd like to contribute tassels!
